{\listtext	\'95	}2 bay leaves\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 4-pound pork {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/loin/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 loin}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons canola oil\
{\listtext	\'95	}Gingered Sweet Potatoes (recipe follows)\
{\listtext	\'95	}Five-Spice Apples (recipe follows)\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 cup {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/chives/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 chives}} cut into 1-inch lengths, for garnish\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons Chile Oil, for {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/garnish/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 garnish}} (recipe follows)\
